Package: TrenchR
Title: Analyse and Plot Trench-like Proxy Records
Version: 1.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Thomas", "Münch", email = "thomas.muench@awi.de",
	role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This R package implements routines targeted at analysing and
    plotting of proxy data derived from spatial arrays of records, specifically
    from trenches. It incorporates the analyses of snow trench stable isotope
    data for the publication of Münch et al., The Cryosphere,
    https://doi.org/10.5194/tc-2017-35, 2017.
Depends: R (>= 3.3.1)
License: GPL (>= 3)
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports:
    geosphere,
    grfxtools (>= 0.5.0),
    prxytools (>= 0.4.0),
    RColorBrewer,
    stattools (>= 0.3.0)
RoxygenNote: 7.2.3
Suggests:
    knitr,
    covr,
    FirnR,
    testthat,
    rmarkdown
BugReports: https://github.com/EarthSystemDiagnostics/TrenchR/issues
VignetteBuilder: knitr
Remotes:
    EarthSystemDiagnostics/grfxtools,
    EarthSystemDiagnostics/stattools,
    EarthSystemDiagnostics/prxytools
